Product Id: Annual Greenhouse, Sod and Nursery Survey
Agriculture and Agri-Food Labour Statistics Program
Includes greenhouse vegetables and greenhouse flowers but excludes cannabis.

Operations which exclusively produce tree seedlings for reforestation are out of scope since the 2016 survey. Prior surveys have included their production, affecting also greenhouse area, production, sales, labour and expenses variables.
Includes all other types of enclosed protection used for growing plants, such as rigid insulation, mine shafts, barns and shelters.
Before 2008, poly-film is included under rigid plastic area.
